metadata.description:
Is it from Soldier Brother?"



Zhang Yuanqing read the letter and frowned.



What is life changing? What do you mean uncontrollable?



Hell, I can't make it clear....... He looked at the black card again, checking it over and over again to make sure it was just an ordinary card, unusual if not unusual, that it felt good and seemed to be of a rare material.



Is it a prime card from some top club? A 36D's little sister is something only a queer man like me can handle.



Lei Yibing is he as a child to play big best friend, xiaobing, two years older than him, grandparents have not bought a new house, two live in an alley.



Thunder a troop speed double A, intelligence C, cover him very much as a child, fight is rushed in front, after being beaten to stay broken, who if laugh at Zhang Yuanqing is the child that does not have father, thunder a soldier can stand for him.



So Zhang Yuanqing always called him soldier brother.
